<p>You said the reasons for it being archived yourself. There were also a number of other reasons (inconsistent archiving standards back then, this being the first recorded surviving tale, etc.) and it's listed on the Archived hub.</p>
<p>It's very easy to add a crosslink to The Warrior and the Dragon, and have that contain a link to this. It'd just need approval from someone higher up, and voila.</p>
<p>As for keeping this? Well, we're not getting rid of archived stuff at the moment. If things change in the future, this will certainly be reviewed, but for now it remains put.</p>

							</div>

								
					
